Construction Projects Engineer
* Candidate must have minimum 5 years experience in installations of interior finishing works, gypsum partitions, wall linings / claddings, suspended ceilings and floors.* Review shop drawings, supervise the project teams to ensure adherence to specifications & drawings.* To coordinate delivery of materials and ensure project completion, within the agreed programs & budgets. *To attend meetings & prepare progress reports. * Fluency in spoken & written English and a valid UAE driving license is essential.* Candidate must be between the age of 30-35.
